<view class="page-root {{isDark ? 'theme-dark' : ''}}">
  <view class="dash-topbar">
    <view class="dash-brand-row" bindtap="onTapProfile">
      <view class="dash-avatar-small">
        <text class="dash-avatar-letter">宝</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dash-brand-text">
        <text class="dash-app-name">育儿笔记</text>
        <text class="dash-app-sub muted-text">Parently · 设置</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="dash-top-actions">
      <view class="dash-icon-btn muted-text" bindtap="onTapBabySetup">新建</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="dash-main">
    <view class="dash-date muted-text">{{dateLine}}</view>
    <view class="dash-hero-title">早安，今天也要温柔记录。</view>
    <view class="dash-hero-lead muted-text">
      宝宝昨夜睡眠连续性不错。下面是过去 24 小时摘要与一周睡眠波动（静态占位数据）。
    </view>

    <view class="insight-card card">
      <view class="insight-badge-row">
        <text class="insight-emoji">◇</text>
        <text class="insight-badge">Daily AI Insight</text>
      </view>
      <view class="insight-headline">午后小睡的固定窗口，往往决定傍晚的情绪底色</view>
      <view class="insight-body muted-text">
        综合近期记录，把午休稳定在 14:00 前后，情绪波动会明显缓和。可在「录入」补充更多细节。
      </view>
      <button class="insight-cta accent-fill-button" bindtap="onTapGoAsk">查看详细分析</button>
    </view>

    <view class="section-row">
      <view class="section-heading">过去 24 小时</view>
      <text class="section-link muted-text" bindtap="onTapGoRecord">查看全部记录</text>
    </view>

    <view class="past-grid">
      <view class="past-cell card" wx:for="{{past24}}" wx:key="label">
        <view class="past-cell-top">
          <text class="past-ico">{{item.icon}}</text>
          <text class="past-time muted-text">{{item.time}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="past-label muted-text">{{item.label}}</view>
        <view class="past-value">{{item.main}}</view>
        <view class="past-sub muted-text">{{item.sub}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="bento-stack">
      <view class="sleep-card card">
        <view class="sleep-head">
          <view>
            <view class="sleep-title">睡眠连续性</view>
            <view class="sleep-sub muted-text">近 7 晚波动</view>
          </view>
          <text class="sleep-more muted-text" bindtap="onTapGoGrowth">···</text>
        </view>
        <view class="sleep-bars">
          <view
            class="sleep-bar-wrap {{item.on ? 'is-on' : ''}}"
            wx:for="{{sleepWeek}}"
            wx:key="d"
          >
            <view class="sleep-bar-h" style="height: {{item.h}}%;"></view>
            <text class="sleep-day {{item.on ? 'sleep-day-on' : ''}}">{{item.d}}</text>
            <text wx:if="{{item.badge}}" class="sleep-badge">{{item.badge}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="mile-card">
        <view class="mile-decor" />
        <view class="mile-body">
          <view class="mile-icon-wrap">
            <text class="mile-spark">✦</text>
          </view>
          <view class="mile-title">即将到来的里程碑</view>
          <view class="mile-desc">
            宝宝正向下一阶段迈进：可留意独坐与对辅食的兴趣（静态演示文案）。
          </view>
          <button class="mile-btn" bindtap="onTapBabySetup">阅读准备指南</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="foot-links muted-text">
      <text class="foot-link" bindtap="onTapProfile">外观与显示</text>
      <text class="foot-dot">·</text>
      <text class="foot-link" bindtap="onTapLogout">退出登录</text>
    </view>

    <view class="dash-foot mono muted-text">
      {{user && user.id ? user.id : '会话就绪 · 演示环境'}}
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
